title: Almost new 3 bedroom unit
posting_body: ['This 3 bedroom light filled upper level unit has a living room, a bathroom and a kitchen.', ' The inside has just been completely redone a few years ago.', ' The bedrooms varied in sizes with the smallest bedroom about 100 square feet and all has closets.', '  It has a smaller living room.', ' The unit has insulation, central heat, LED lighting, tankless water heater and fire sprinklers.', 'There is street parking only.', 'Owner pays for garbage and fire alarm monitoring.', 'Tenant pays water and PGE.', 'Move in cost is 1 month rent plus $3,400 security deposit', 'Available now', 'Need full credit report and proof of income', 'Shown by appointment only', 'One year lease', 'Sorry no pets', 'The location is at 785 Treat Ave. between 20th and 21st Street in the Mission District.', '  It is close to many conveniences in the area such as transportation, shopping and restaurants.']
